README.md
     1→# humanize
     2→
     3→[![PyPI version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/humanize.svg?logo=pypi&logoColor=FFE873)](https://pypi.org/project/humanize/)
     4→[![Supported Python versions](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/humanize.svg?logo=python&logoColor=FFE873)](https://pypi.org/project/humanize/)
     5→[![Documentation Status](https://readthedocs.org/projects/python-humanize/badge/?version=latest)](https://humanize.readthedocs.io/en/latest/?badge=latest)
     6→[![PyPI downloads](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/humanize.svg)](https://pypistats.org/packages/humanize)
